The issuance of bonds and notes totaling up to, but not exceeding, ten (10)
percent of the current year's tax levy for any single purpose in any one Fiscal Year
may, after public hearing and approval of the Board of Finance, be authorized by
vote of the Town Meeting pursuant to Chapter III of this Charter.
